  "Aftersales Pairing : BCM": {
   "width": 10980,
   "height": 9780,
   "color": "rgb(128,0,128)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Protected Pairing : BCM pairing in After Sales ",
     "color": "rgb(232,191,224)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,128)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 105,
      "top": 45,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10815
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure :",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 1440,
      "height": 5040,
      "width": 10800
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) !! Check that you have access rights to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\"",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 1680,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 7920
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Press \"Request Server BCM pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 2040,
      "height": 255,
      "width": 9600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Select the \"Input Data Server\" (19 bytes) and copy it in the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\".  ",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 3000,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 9480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Get the \"Server answer\" (16 bytes) and copy it in this screen. Then press \"Transmit Server Answer\" ",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 3240,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) If the BCM is SA unlocked for BCM pairing then :",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 4320,
      "height": 1200,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID / BCM information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6120,
      "top": 6600,
      "height": 3000,
      "width": 4800
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " CID ANALYSE - Select \"startRoutine\" and press the button",
     "color": "rgb(128,0,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 480,
      "height": 960,
      "width": 10800
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA failure ",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
