    },
    {
     "text": "2) Check that the ECM is blank (try to start the vehicle) and read the ECM information \" ECM_IS_BLANK\"",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 1320,
      "height": 285,
      "width": 8775
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Press the button \"Request Server ECM pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 1680,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 8790
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Select the \"Input Data to Server\" (19 bytes) and copy it in the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\".  ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 2040,
      "height": 255,
      "width": 8775
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) Complete the frames in the application and press the button \"Calcul\".Get the \"Server answer\" (16 bytes) and copy it in this screen. Then press the button \"Transmit Server Answer\" ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 2880,
      "height": 615,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) !! Check that you have access rights to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\"",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 840,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 10020
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) If the BCM is SA unlocked for ECM pairing then put the Ignition Power Supply OFF, select \"startRoutine\" and press the button \"Authorize ECM pairing\" ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 4800,
      "height": 885,
      "width": 11520
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "7) If the authorization to pair is TRUE, then switch Ignition Power Supply ON. If the ECM is paired, procedure exit is automatic.",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 6360,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 10080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "ECM / BCM information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6120,
      "top": 7200,
      "height": 2520,
      "width": 5760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA failure ",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 7200,
      "height": 2520,
      "width": 5880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "8) To postpone the authorization to pair the ECM, press the button ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 6720,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "return code",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 4020,
      "top": 5550,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 720
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial Narrow",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA Unlocked for ECM pairing",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 945,
      "top": 4365,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 3495
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Authorization to pair ECM",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
