  "Rework or AfterSales Pairing : BCM or CID": {
   "width": 11700,
   "height": 11340,
   "color": "rgb(64,128,128)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "FACTORY REWORK / AFTERSALES : BCM or Customer ID pairing  ",
     "color": "rgb(184,220,220)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 120,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11400
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure",
     "color": "rgb(184,220,220)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 1920,
      "height": 1605,
      "width": 11400
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) Complete the \"After Sales code\" ( 16 bytes), select \"StartRoutine\" and press \"ENTER REWORK/AFTERSALES MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(184,220,220)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 2520,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 11160
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the REWORK/AFTERSALES MODE for BCM pairing is launched, then",
     "color": "rgb(184,220,220)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 4320,
      "height": 720,
      "width": 5280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Once all the customer IDs are paired, press the button \"EXIT REWORK/ AFTERSALES MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(184,220,220)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 5520,
      "top": 6240,
      "height": 840,
      "width": 6000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID / BCM information",
     "color": "rgb(184,220,220)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6720,
      "top": 7200,
      "height": 2160,
      "width": 4770
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID ANALYSE - Select \"StartRoutine\" and press the button",
     "color": "rgb(184,220,220)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 600,
      "height": 1335,
      "width": 11400
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Pairing information",
     "color": "rgb(184,220,220)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 9120,
      "height": 2160,
      "width": 6480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Rework Mode failure ",
     "color": "rgb(184,220,220)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 7200,
      "height": 1815,
      "width": 6480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Select\"StartRoutine\" and press \"CID Pairing\" to pair a key",
     "color": "rgb(184,220,220)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 5520,
      "top": 5040,
      "height": 1560,
      "width": 6000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the REWORK/AFTERSALES MODE for customer ID pairing is launched, then",
     "color": "rgb(184,220,220)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 5520,
      "top": 4320,
      "height": 720,
      "width": 6000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Select \"StartRoutine\" and press \"BCM pairing\" to pair the BCM",
     "color": "rgb(184,220,220)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 5040,
      "height": 1440,
      "width": 5280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) If the BCM is paired, the EXIT of the REWORK/AFTERSALES MODE is automatic. Then pair all Keys (procedure in right)",
